  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the broiler.",
    "In a medium bowl, whisk together flour, garlic powder, onion powder, black pepper, and salt.",
    "Add the feta cheese, thyme, and Greek yogurt to the bowl and mix until well combined.",
    "Add the olive oil and honey to the bowl and mix until the cheese is coated.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "Dot the top of the mixture with butter.",
    "Broil the mixture for 5-7 minutes, or until the top is golden brown and the cheese is melted.",
    "Remove the dish from the oven and let it cool for a few minutes.",
    "Drizzle the white vinegar over the top of the gratin before serving.",
    "Serve warm, garnished with additional thyme if desired."
  ],
